message.entry: Inputs A, B must be sparse matrices.
Inputs A, B must have dimensions compatible for matrix multiplication.
Input maxNz must be a real scalar.
Input maxNz must be nonnegative and less than 2^48-1.
Input threadChoice must be 0 (default heuristic), 1 (multithreaded), or 2 (single threaded).
Input wkspChoice must be 0 (default heuristic), 1 (vector), or 2 (unordered set).
